<br>
Thank you for your time. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=hatfull>hatfull</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/11/01 12:09:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=320.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rogue guilds on Tallon Zek?</span><hr size=1> and I forgot to ask. But, once Ive earned a lvl of 20 or so, or whereever, are they any Rogue guilds which cater only to the Evil Rogue.  <br>
