Thank you again. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufricka.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fricka</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.thesafehouse.org/~fricka/shanks/teenyknot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/11/01 12:27:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=320.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/~fricka/7summerfricka.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rogue guilds on Tallon Zek?</span><hr size=1> I don't beleive there are any there. I know that the Order of The Black Rose has a guild on Rallos and Vallon, but not on Tallon Zek.<br>
