rrently), depends on your ability to be utterly charming, even to the less civil people you will meet.  If you can't bite your tongue when some druid sends you a tell &quot;U R Ghey and U suxors U fagoot&quot;, then I would suggest finding a guild to back you up.  There are hordes of obnoxious little 12 year olds on the server that like to gang up guildless people, because they are safe easy targets. <p><img src=http://members.home.net/atsila/pictures/Malsig.jpg></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufricka.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fricka</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.thesafehouse.org/~fricka/shanks/teenyknot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/12/01 12:42:54 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=320.topic&index=5>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rogue guilds on Tallon Zek?</span><hr size=1> You're welcome, Hatful, and good luck! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usepsisletalis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SepsisLetalis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/12/01 2:28:05 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=320.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> HI